### Create customer
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/customers
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Slug: acme
X-Correlation-Id: demo-create-customer-001

{
  "externalId": "customer-1001",
  "email": "USER1001@example.com",
  "fullName": "User 1001",
  "plan": "PREMIUM"
}

### List customers
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/customers?page=0&size=10
X-Tenant-Slug: acme
X-Correlation-Id: demo-list-customers-001

### Duplicate customer by external id or email
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/customers
Content-Type: application/json
X-Tenant-Slug: acme
X-Correlation-Id: demo-duplicate-customer-001

{
  "externalId": "customer-1001",
  "email": "user1001@example.com",
  "fullName": "Duplicate User",
  "plan": "FREE"
}

### Missing tenant header
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/customers
X-Correlation-Id: demo-customers-missing-tenant-001